Job DetailsBe a part of our exciting restaurant, Empress by Boon, located in the heart of Chinatown! We are looking to add new team members. If you are interested in joining us as we build an exciting new destination for San Francisco diners, please apply.  Our ideal candidates are those who:

have previous restaurant experience, but willing to train the right individual;
Have a passion for hospitality and the desire to create unique experiences for all of their guests;
Come offering solutions to challenges they face;
Love the excitement of the restaurnat industry;
Have attention to detail;
Have a flexible schedule, including nights and weekends, as well as the occasional Holiday.

